1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 16=

3
00:00:45,860 --> 00:00:47,340
The name Gu Nianchi

4
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:49,340
stopped being my name long ago.

5
00:00:50,460 --> 00:00:52,260
Ever since my mother passed away,

6
00:00:53,940 --> 00:00:55,380
I've been called Lu Shaoyuan.

7
00:00:57,580 --> 00:00:59,140
It's really hard for me to imagine

8
00:01:00,140 --> 00:01:02,860
that you and he are brothers
born of the same mother.

9
00:01:03,660 --> 00:01:05,580
How could he possibly replace you?

10
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:08,220
And how could he bear

11
00:01:08,660 --> 00:01:10,340
to let your mother die?

12
00:01:11,260 --> 00:01:12,179
We were originally born

13
00:01:12,180 --> 00:01:13,540
into a fairly decent family.

14
00:01:15,020 --> 00:01:16,419
But after our father passed away,

15
00:01:16,420 --> 00:01:17,780
our family fell into ruin.

16
00:01:18,820 --> 00:01:19,979
Mother took us

17
00:01:19,980 --> 00:01:21,540
and wandered into a village.

18
00:01:22,100 --> 00:01:23,420
From then on,

19
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,100
Mother's health worsened day by day.

20
00:01:27,820 --> 00:01:29,500
To earn money for Mother's treatment,

21
00:01:30,860 --> 00:01:32,140
I enlisted in the army.

22
00:01:33,940 --> 00:01:35,420
Because of my military achievements,

23
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:37,660
and because I
accidentally saved Li Shuche,

24
00:01:38,780 --> 00:01:40,220
I was promoted to Commander.

25
00:01:41,100 --> 00:01:42,820
But I never expected that
on my way home,

26
00:01:43,340 --> 00:01:44,780
I'd be ambushed by attackers,

27
00:01:45,420 --> 00:01:46,700
nearly lose my life,

28
00:01:46,940 --> 00:01:48,340
and temporarily lose my sight.

29
00:01:50,380 --> 00:01:52,090
That was when

30
00:01:52,700 --> 00:01:54,560
Gu Shaoyan replaced me.

31
00:02:00,020 --> 00:02:01,020
It's him.

32
00:02:01,060 --> 00:02:02,140
It must be him.

33
00:02:02,420 --> 00:02:02,779
Quick.

34
00:02:02,780 --> 00:02:03,699
Bring him to me.

35
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:04,260
Yes.

36
00:02:05,580 --> 00:02:06,380
Gu Nianchi.

37
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,720
Gu Nianchi. The Commander-in-Chief
is looking for you.

38
00:02:09,900 --> 00:02:10,660
Please.

39
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:15,740
Nianchi.

40
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:17,780
So it really is you.

41
00:02:18,260 --> 00:02:19,299
You are...

42
00:02:19,300 --> 00:02:21,020
I've finally found you.

43
00:02:23,820 --> 00:02:24,539
Nianchi,

44
00:02:24,540 --> 00:02:26,739
because of your
outstanding military achievements,

45
00:02:26,740 --> 00:02:28,739
I've personally come to promote you

46
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:30,180
to Commander of Yancheng.

47
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:38,380
Thanks, Commander-in-Chief.

48
00:02:39,020 --> 00:02:40,540
What are you thanking me for?

49
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:42,259
You saved my life.

50
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:44,340
I haven't even thanked you properly yet.

51
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:46,180
Oh, right.

52
00:02:46,260 --> 00:02:48,580
Who else is left in your family?
Bring all of them here.

53
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:53,640
My whole family is dead.

54
00:02:54,060 --> 00:02:55,020
I'm the only one left.

55
00:02:55,540 --> 00:02:57,100
So that's how it is.

56
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:58,740
Nianchi,

57
00:02:59,260 --> 00:03:00,980
would you be willing

58
00:03:01,180 --> 00:03:03,580
to become my adopted son?

59
00:03:07,260 --> 00:03:08,140
Father.

60
00:03:10,740 --> 00:03:11,779
Come.

61
00:03:11,780 --> 00:03:12,780
Get up.

62
00:03:13,140 --> 00:03:14,339
All right, let's go.

63
00:03:14,340 --> 00:03:15,260
Shaoyan.

64
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:18,419
Where's Godmother's medicine?

65
00:03:18,420 --> 00:03:19,220
This...

66
00:03:19,540 --> 00:03:20,900
He's just some street punk.

67
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:21,899
Let's go, Father.

68
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:22,660
All right.

69
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:23,540
Yes.

70
00:03:24,660 --> 00:03:25,620
Shaoyan.

71
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:28,179
Shaoyan.

72
00:03:28,180 --> 00:03:29,900
Godmother's medicine. Don't go!

73
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:32,339
After Gu Shaoyan used your name

74
00:03:32,340 --> 00:03:33,820
to become Commander,

75
00:03:33,980 --> 00:03:36,820
because my father refused to help
Commander-in-Chief Li traffic opium,

76
00:03:37,220 --> 00:03:39,500
he secretly withheld
one of his opium shipments.

77
00:03:40,020 --> 00:03:43,139
So he joined forces
with Zhuang Xun and Lily

78
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:44,340
to frame my family together.

79
00:03:45,220 --> 00:03:46,820
He executed my whole family.

80
00:03:49,780 --> 00:03:51,580
He shot me once too.

81
00:03:52,220 --> 00:03:54,060
But heaven had other plans.

82
00:03:57,580 --> 00:03:59,140
The jade pendant you gave me

83
00:04:00,140 --> 00:04:01,780
blocked that bullet for me.

84
00:04:04,140 --> 00:04:06,260
I had someone repair it afterward.

85
00:04:08,180 --> 00:04:09,860
So the person who sent me the letter

86
00:04:09,900 --> 00:04:11,860
saying Zhuang Xun
was at Golden Melody Love Songs

87
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:13,060
really was you.

88
00:04:13,100 --> 00:04:13,860
That's right.

89
00:04:14,860 --> 00:04:15,860
At the time,

90
00:04:16,180 --> 00:04:18,220
I wanted to use Gu Shaoyan's hand

91
00:04:18,260 --> 00:04:19,940
to kill the traitor
of the Zhuang family.

92
00:04:22,620 --> 00:04:24,020
After you left that day,

93
00:04:24,460 --> 00:04:25,860
Cheng Yi found me

94
00:04:28,220 --> 00:04:29,780
and told me my mother had passed away.

95
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:34,420
So I had no choice but to leave
without saying goodbye.

96
00:04:40,140 --> 00:04:41,940
If he hadn't replaced me back then,

97
00:04:44,180 --> 00:04:45,700
your family wouldn't have suffered.

98
00:04:48,340 --> 00:04:49,740
How can you blame yourself for that?

99
00:04:50,140 --> 00:04:51,540
You're kind by nature.

100
00:04:51,740 --> 00:04:53,620
With you as the Commander
of Yancheng from now on,

101
00:04:53,980 --> 00:04:55,860
you'll definitely protect Yancheng well.

102
00:04:59,940 --> 00:05:00,860
By the way, Darling,

103
00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:03,459
Cheng Yi and I previously discovered

104
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:05,920
that the clue about the Zhuang family
hiding that shipment of opium

105
00:05:06,580 --> 00:05:07,900
was connected to a flower.

106
00:05:08,700 --> 00:05:11,540
Do you know what flower it was?

107
00:05:22,700 --> 00:05:23,460
Look.

108
00:05:30,180 --> 00:05:31,380
So this was it.

109
00:05:32,460 --> 00:05:34,060
I thought of it before too.

110
00:05:35,340 --> 00:05:36,780
But I just couldn't figure out

111
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:39,300
what secret was hidden here.

112
00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:43,940
The scar really is still here.

113
00:05:44,780 --> 00:05:46,420
But back at Paramount,

114
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:49,060
why didn't I notice it?

115
00:05:50,220 --> 00:05:51,739
That day at Paramount,

116
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:53,900
it was because
of the special angle and lighting.

117
00:05:56,140 --> 00:05:57,860
How is my wife so smart?

118
00:06:01,900 --> 00:06:03,340
Back then,

119
00:06:04,180 --> 00:06:05,659
my father hid that harmful shipment

120
00:06:05,660 --> 00:06:07,580
in an extremely secret place.

121
00:06:08,140 --> 00:06:11,219
Then he hid the location

122
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:12,620
inside this flower.

123
00:06:13,340 --> 00:06:14,620
The secret lies in

124
00:06:14,740 --> 00:06:16,500
the varying flower petals

125
00:06:16,780 --> 00:06:18,180
and dotted stamens.

126
00:06:20,060 --> 00:06:21,459
This is Morse code.

127
00:06:21,460 --> 00:06:22,460
That's right.

128
00:06:23,660 --> 00:06:25,579
Before my father died,

129
00:06:25,580 --> 00:06:27,460
I got the pattern
of the red spider lily.

130
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:30,340
But I was worried it might fall
into the wrong hands again.

131
00:06:30,660 --> 00:06:31,980
After thinking it over,

132
00:06:32,860 --> 00:06:34,460
I tattooed it onto my body.

133
00:06:35,100 --> 00:06:37,219
I planned that
once everything settled down,

134
00:06:37,220 --> 00:06:38,580
I'd find that shipment of opium

135
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:39,980
and destroy it

136
00:06:40,300 --> 00:06:41,560
when the time came.

137
00:06:42,780 --> 00:06:43,620
Shaoyuan.

138
00:06:56,740 --> 00:06:57,380
Shaoyuan.

139
00:06:58,020 --> 00:06:59,060
Yunqiu is awake?

140
00:06:59,180 --> 00:07:00,140
Hello, Yunqiu.

141
00:07:03,140 --> 00:07:03,579
Shaoyuan,

142
00:07:03,580 --> 00:07:04,419
that military seal

143
00:07:04,420 --> 00:07:06,180
has already been hidden
where you instructed.

144
00:07:06,220 --> 00:07:08,640
I guarantee that besides you and me,
no one else will find it.

145
00:07:09,020 --> 00:07:09,820
Good.

146
00:07:12,780 --> 00:07:14,940
Can you tie your tie properly?

147
00:07:15,180 --> 00:07:18,060
You're already serving as an adjutant.
Pay more attention to your image.

148
00:07:18,100 --> 00:07:19,840
Haven't I always been like this?

149
00:07:20,140 --> 00:07:21,059
What?

150
00:07:21,060 --> 00:07:22,939
Now that you have Yunqiu,
you find me annoying?

151
00:07:22,940 --> 00:07:24,360
What nonsense are you talking about?

152
00:07:25,100 --> 00:07:26,440
You'll always be my little brother.

153
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,180
All right.

154
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,480
Where did this sachet come from?

155
00:07:31,660 --> 00:07:33,040
Xinran just gave it to me.

156
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:35,040
She said it was to congratulate me
on becoming an adjutant.

157
00:07:35,460 --> 00:07:36,340
If you like it,

158
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,459
I'll give it to you.

159
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:38,660
No.

160
00:07:40,540 --> 00:07:42,580
You really haven't figured
women out at all.

161
00:07:45,940 --> 00:07:46,660
Anything else?

162
00:07:46,820 --> 00:07:47,620
Nothing.

163
00:07:51,900 --> 00:07:52,820
I'm leaving.

164
00:07:53,460 --> 00:07:54,740
Goodbye, Yunqiu.

165
00:08:16,580 --> 00:08:17,580
Have some water.

166
00:08:17,780 --> 00:08:18,780
Thank you.

167
00:08:27,700 --> 00:08:29,299
Something as important
as the military seal,

168
00:08:29,300 --> 00:08:30,740
is it really okay

169
00:08:30,820 --> 00:08:31,780
to leave it to him?

170
00:08:33,340 --> 00:08:34,300
Don't worry.

171
00:08:34,700 --> 00:08:36,840
He's my brother who's gone through
life and death with me.

172
00:08:37,620 --> 00:08:38,880
Other than you,

173
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:40,860
he's the only family

174
00:08:41,180 --> 00:08:42,260
I have left in this world.

175
00:09:03,580 --> 00:09:05,140
Tonight I'll take Yunqiu out first.

176
00:09:05,820 --> 00:09:06,940
Go make the arrangements now.

177
00:09:07,300 --> 00:09:08,640
Don't worry.

178
00:09:08,980 --> 00:09:11,660
I couldn't tell
you were actually this romantic.

179
00:09:11,780 --> 00:09:13,099
Keep your voice down.

180
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:14,459
But let's agree on this first.

181
00:09:14,460 --> 00:09:15,759
I'm reserving the position

182
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:17,060
of your future child's godfather.

183
00:09:17,260 --> 00:09:19,820
I'll teach the kid how to shoot too,
just like you taught me.

184
00:09:20,980 --> 00:09:23,990
You should find my child
a godmother first.

185
00:09:24,900 --> 00:09:26,600
Don't worry.

186
00:09:26,820 --> 00:09:28,539
In the future, I'll learn from you too.

187
00:09:28,540 --> 00:09:30,459
I'll do something romantic for her

188
00:09:30,460 --> 00:09:32,199
so my future wife

189
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,620
will never forget it.

190
00:09:33,860 --> 00:09:34,580
All right.

191
00:09:35,340 --> 00:09:36,620
Once you find someone you like,

192
00:09:37,020 --> 00:09:39,499
I will arrange something
even grander than this for you.

193
00:09:39,500 --> 00:09:40,580
Forget it.

194
00:09:41,500 --> 00:09:43,580
I'd rather save up some money first,

195
00:09:44,020 --> 00:09:45,419
buy a big house,

196
00:09:45,420 --> 00:09:46,780
and then get married.

197
00:09:48,860 --> 00:09:49,700
I'm leaving.

198
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:51,660
Yi.

199
00:09:52,420 --> 00:09:53,540
What's wrong?

200
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:55,379
Be careful on the road.

201
00:09:55,380 --> 00:09:56,180
Come back early.

202
00:09:57,060 --> 00:09:58,189
Got it.

203
00:09:58,190 --> 00:09:59,820
I'm not a child anymore.

204
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:02,360
No matter how old you are,
you'll always be my little brother.

205
00:10:02,620 --> 00:10:03,540
Got it.

206
00:10:04,380 --> 00:10:05,940
Mission guaranteed.

207
00:10:32,020 --> 00:10:32,940
Darling,

208
00:10:33,140 --> 00:10:33,779
I know

209
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:35,510
you're still worried about Xue Wan.

210
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:38,900
Once I finish dealing with the opium matter,
we'll go apologize to her properly,

211
00:10:38,980 --> 00:10:39,660
all right?

212
00:10:40,220 --> 00:10:40,900
Mm.

213
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:57,810
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

214
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:04,440
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

215
00:11:04,940 --> 00:11:08,520
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

216
00:11:08,860 --> 00:11:11,870
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

217
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:17,160
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

218
00:11:18,280 --> 00:11:23,470
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

219
00:11:24,530 --> 00:11:30,130
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

220
00:11:30,670 --> 00:11:34,050
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

221
00:11:34,300 --> 00:11:37,249
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

222
00:11:37,250 --> 00:11:42,389
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

223
00:11:42,390 --> 00:11:46,709
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

224
00:11:46,710 --> 00:11:49,289
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

225
00:11:49,290 --> 00:11:51,569
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

226
00:11:51,570 --> 00:11:55,119
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

227
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:59,649
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

228
00:11:59,650 --> 00:12:02,180
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

229
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:04,269
♪Still I walk into♪

230
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:07,869
♪The trap you set without regret♪

231
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:11,919
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

232
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:14,499
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

233
00:12:14,500 --> 00:12:16,659
♪A stand in can never cross♪

234
00:12:16,660 --> 00:12:20,099
♪The shortest distance between us♪

235
00:12:20,100 --> 00:12:25,070
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

236
00:12:25,230 --> 00:12:29,900
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

237
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:34,249
♪A substitute♪

238
00:12:34,250 --> 00:12:39,250
♪Needs no reason♪

